name: Cisco | IOS | Environment | Temperature Out of Range #8 (SYSLOG)
description: %UBR7200-0-TEMPHIGH : [chars] measured at [chars] is too high: shutdown temperature [chars]

patterns.value_re: %UBR\d+00-0-TEMPHIGH\s*: \S+ measured at (?P<name>\S+) is too (?P<threshold>high): shutdown temperature (?P<max>\S+)
